title: 2014 Thai FA Cup
text:
The 2014 <a href="Thai%20FA%20Cup">Thai FA Cup</a> () is the 19th season of <a href="Thailand">Thailand</a> knockout <a href="Association%20football">football</a> competition. The tournament is organized by the <a href="Football%20Association%20of%20Thailand">Football Association of Thailand</a>.
The cup winner is guaranteed a place in the <a href="2015%20AFC%20Champions%20League">2015 AFC Champions League Play-off</a>.
Results.
Preliminary round.
The preliminary round consists of two rounds for teams currently playing in the <a href="Regional%20League%20Division%202">Regional League Division 2</a> level. The first round was held on 19 March 2014.
